<plot>Beloved spiritual teacher Ram Dass spent a day visiting with the staff and patients at Spaulding Rehabilitation Hospital in Boston. In a video of his visit there, Ram Dass talks about the effects of his stroke, his relationships with his caretakers, and how his illness has influenced his spiritual life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?510716</url></doc>
